        "description": "Instantly immerse yourself in your haptic creations designed in Meta Haptics studio with the VR companion App, providing real-time feedback without the need for code or building your application.\n\nThe Auditioning App is part of a suite of haptics tools, Meta Haptics Studio and Meta Haptics SDK. These tools allow both designers and developers to quickly and easily create, audition and implement high-quality HD haptics from your existing audio effects.\n1. Design haptic effects in Meta Haptics Studio Desktop\n2. Audition effects with VR Companion App\n3. Export .haptic clips from Desktop App\n4. Integrate haptic effects with Haptics SDK for Unity, Unreal, or Native\n\nKey features:\n- Real-time Design Validation: Feel your creations instantly, allowing you to fine-tune and validate your designs in real time without the need for code or to build your application.\n- Extensive Haptic Sample Library: Dive into our comprehensive library of haptic effects for inspiration\n- Mute Audio/Haptic: Eliminate audio distractions and focus on your haptic creations\n- Pin projects to locally store them on your device for seamless workflow management\n",
